<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 05 Jan 2025 01:12:46 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国市场大火造成8人死亡、15人受伤</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-market-blaze-kills-eight-15-hurt-2025-01-04/</link><description>据中央电视台周六报道，中国北部省份河北省的一个菜市场发生火灾，造成 8 人死亡、15 人受伤。</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 Jan 2025 09:05:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-market-blaze-kills-eight-15-hurt-2025-01-04/</guid></item><item><title>美国国家安全顾问访问印度讨论中国水坝问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinese-dams-be-discussed-during-india-visit-us-national-security-adviser-2025-01-03/</link><description>华盛顿及其西方盟友长期以来一直将印度视为中国在亚洲及其他地区影响力不断上升的对手。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 22:17:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinese-dams-be-discussed-during-india-visit-us-national-security-adviser-2025-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>美国因涉嫌黑客攻击而制裁中国诚信科技</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/us-issues-cybersecurity-sanctions-against-chinas-integrity-technology-2025-01-03/</link><description>美国周五制裁了中国诚信科技集团，指责其是一个名为“亚麻台风”的多产黑客组织的幕后黑手。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 15:50:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/us-issues-cybersecurity-sanctions-against-chinas-integrity-technology-2025-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>印度表示已向中国转达了对西藏水电站大坝的担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-says-conveyed-concerns-china-over-hydropower-dam-tibet-2025-01-03/</link><description>中国官员表示，西藏水电项目不会对环境或下游水源产生重大影响。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 11:12:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-says-conveyed-concerns-china-over-hydropower-dam-tibet-2025-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>中国为政府工作人员提供十年来首次大幅加薪以提振经济</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-gives-government-workers-first-big-pay-bump-decade-boost-economy-2025-01-03/</link><description>受此举影响的人士表示，中国各地数百万政府工作人员本周意外加薪，因为北京方面希望增加支出以支持经济放缓。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 07:19:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-gives-government-workers-first-big-pay-bump-decade-boost-economy-2025-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>中国设立新的国家体育仲裁中心</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-sets-up-new-national-sports-arbitration-centre-2025-01-03/</link><description>中国本周在首都北京开设了首个国家体育仲裁中心，为加强解决体育纠纷和保护运动员权利的法律框架迈出了关键一步。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 06:45:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-sets-up-new-national-sports-arbitration-centre-2025-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>在商业航空经历了致命的一年之后，中国敦促进行安全评估</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-urges-safety-assessments-after-deadly-year-commercial-aviation-2025-01-03/</link><description>继2018年以来全球商业航空死亡人数最多的一年之后，中国当局呼吁对行业风险进行评估，以发现从航线到跑道的任何“隐藏”运营风险。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 05:49:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-urges-safety-assessments-after-deadly-year-commercial-aviation-2025-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>2025年中国将大幅增加国债融资刺激经济增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-will-sharply-increase-funding-treasury-bonds-spur-growth-2025-2025-01-03/</link><description>一位国家规划官员周五表示，中国将在 2025 年大幅增加超长期国债资金，以刺激商业投资和消费刺激计划，同时北京将加大财政刺激力度，以重振步履蹒跚的经济。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 04:22:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-will-sharply-increase-funding-treasury-bonds-spur-growth-2025-2025-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>海南免税消费大幅下滑，中国购物天堂陷入困境</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/trouble-chinas-shopping-paradise-hainan-duty-free-spending-falls-29-2025-01-03/</link><description>去年，由于经济疲软导致国内游客数量急剧下降，LVMH 和开云集团等全球奢侈品牌都在中国海南省开设了商店，免税支出下降了 29.3%。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 02:41:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/trouble-chinas-shopping-paradise-hainan-duty-free-spending-falls-29-2025-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>中国央行表示将适时降低银行存款准备金率</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-central-bank-might-cut-interest-rates-current-level-15-2025-ft-reports-2025-01-03/</link><description>根据周五发布的一份声明，中国央行表示将在上周举行的货币政策委员会季度会议上“适时”下调银行存款准备金率和利率。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 00:20:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-central-bank-might-cut-interest-rates-current-level-15-2025-ft-reports-2025-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>英国立法者传唤 Shein 和 Temu 询问其劳工行为</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/uk-lawmakers-summon-shein-temu-questioning-over-labour-practices-2025-01-02/</link><description>希望在伦敦上市的快时尚在线零售商 Shein 将于 1 月 7 日在英国举行听证会，英国议会委员会计划就这家 2008 年在中国成立的公司供应链中工人的权利提出质疑。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 17:12:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/uk-lawmakers-summon-shein-temu-questioning-over-labour-practices-2025-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国提议进一步限制电池、关键矿产技术的出口</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/china-proposes-further-export-curbs-battery-critical-minerals-tech-2025-01-02/</link><description>周四发布的一份文件显示，中国商务部已提议对一些用于制造电池组件和加工关键矿物锂和镓的技术实施出口限制。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 15:10:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/china-proposes-further-export-curbs-battery-critical-minerals-tech-2025-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>美国考虑制定限制或禁止中国无人机的潜在规则</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-considers-potential-rules-restrict-or-bar-chinese-drones-2025-01-02/</link><description>美国商务部周四表示，正在考虑制定新规则，对中国无人机实施限制，以国家安全考虑为由限制或禁止中国无人机在美国销售。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 10:07:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-considers-potential-rules-restrict-or-bar-chinese-drones-2025-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国将28家美国实体列入出口管制名单</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/china-adds-28-us-entities-export-control-list-2025-01-02/</link><description>中国商务部周四表示，中国已将 28 家美国实体列入出口管制清单，以“维护国家安全和利益”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 08:21:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/china-adds-28-us-entities-export-control-list-2025-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国卫健委将缩小精神卫生服务差距</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-health-commission-narrow-gaps-mental-health-services-2025-01-02/</link><description>中国国家卫生健康委员会表示，随着当局努力解决越来越多的心理健康问题，特别是儿童和青少年的心理健康问题，中国国家卫生健康委员会将在2025年至2027年期间解决心理健康服务方面的差距。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 05:57:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-health-commission-narrow-gaps-mental-health-services-2025-01-02/</guid></item></channel></rss>